name: #11 Cefrey Stormwind
description:
Cefrey Stormwind

Race: Human

Subraces and Variants:
Ethnicity: Illuskan
Dragonmark Variant: Mark of Handling

Physical Characteristics:
Age: 35 years
Height: 5'6"
Weight: 140 lbs.
Eyes: Blue
Skin: Dark Brown

Gender: Female
Class: Rogue
Roguish Archetype: Arcane Trickster
Background: Charlatan
Occupation: Farmer or herder

Trait: I have a joke for every occasion, especially occasions where humor is inappropriate.
Ideal: Aspiration. I'm determined to make something of myself. (Any)
Bond: I come from a noble family, and one day I'll reclaim my lands and title from those who stole them from me.
Flaw: I'm convinced that no one could ever fool me the way I fool others.

Description:
Appearance: Pronounced scar
High Ability: Dexterity-lithe, agile, graceful
Low Ability: Constitution-sickly, pale
Talent: Great at impersonations
Mannerism: Enunciates overly clearly
Interaction Trait: Suspicious
Values: Slaughter (Evil), Protective of colleagues or compatriots, Loyal to a benefactor, patron, or employer
Flaw or Secret: Specific phobia
